high_descs: Go forward and hang a left, go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, take the egg out of the microwave and close the door.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn right towards the leftmost sink.
Put the egg in the leftmost sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn around and cross the room to the white table that has the coffee maker on it.
Put the egg on the table at the bottom of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Take the egg from the microwave.
Look down to face the sink on the left.
Wash the egg in the sink, then pick it up again.
Turn around and walk to the table behind you.
Place the egg on the table, in front of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg on a table.

high_descs: turn left and head for the microwave
take out an egg from the microwave
move towards the sink under the microwave
place the egg in the sink and cool it with water
turn around towards the dining table
drop the egg on the dining table
anns.task_desc: drop a cool egg on the dining table
